devdoc.author: Set Protocol Module that enables managers to absorb tokens sent to the SetToken into the token's positions. With each SetToken, managers are able to specify 1) the airdrops they want to include, 2) an airdrop fee recipient, 3) airdrop fee, and 4) whether all users are allowed to trigger an airdrop.

returns._0: Array of tokens approved for airdrops

params._airdropSettings: Struct of airdrop setting for Set including accepted airdrops, feeRecipient,                                  airdropFee, and indicating if anyone can call an absorb

params._newFee: Percentage, in preciseUnits, of new airdrop fee (1e16 = 1%)

devdoc.title: AirdropModule

absorb(address,address).notice: Absorb specified token into position. If airdropFee defined, send portion to feeRecipient and portion to protocol feeRecipient address. Callable only by manager unless manager has set anyoneAbsorb to true.

addAirdrop(address,address).notice: SET MANAGER ONLY. Adds new tokens to be added to positions when absorb is called.

batchAbsorb(address,address[]).notice: Absorb passed tokens into respective positions. If airdropFee defined, send portion to feeRecipient and portion to protocol feeRecipient address. Callable only by manager unless manager has set anyoneAbsorb to true.

getAirdrops(address).notice: Get list of tokens approved to collect airdrops for the SetToken.

initialize(address,(address[],address,ui.notice: SET MANAGER ONLY. Initialize module with SetToken and set initial airdrop tokens as well as specify whether anyone can call absorb.

isAirdropToken(address,address).notice: Get boolean indicating if token is approved for airdrops.

removeAirdrop(address,address).notice: SET MANAGER ONLY. Removes tokens from list to be absorbed.

removeModule().notice: Removes this module from the SetToken, via call by the SetToken. Token's airdrop settings are deleted. Airdrops are not absorbed.

updateAirdropFee(address,uint256).notice: SET MANAGER ONLY. Update airdrop fee percentage.

updateAnyoneAbsorb(address).notice: SET MANAGER ONLY. Update whether manager allows other addresses to call absorb.

updateFeeRecipient(address,address).notice: SET MANAGER ONLY. Update address manager fees are sent to.
